<div style="width: 600px; max-height: 550px; overflow-x: auto;"><h1 class="green b_mar_ten">JOURNEY TO THE INNER LIGHT</h1>
	<p class="size11"><strong>Room: 3AB</strong><em><br/>Start: 5:00PM<br/>End: 5:55PM</em></p><br/>
	<p class="rte">Hugo Award winning writer<b> Morgan Gendel</b> talks about "The Inner Light", the #1 fan favorite episode of Star Trek: The Next Generation. Accompanied by clips from the episode, Morgan will talk about how he got the idea for "The Inner Light" as well as discuss how he developed the episode with the young ST:TNG producers who are now household names to Trek fans. Subjects will include his post-TNG work as the writer-producer of more than 200 episodes of primetime TV plus a sneak preview of his current movie project with Stan Lee.</p></div>